#: src/qml/Settings/PlaybackSettings.qml:107
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Hardware decoding"
msgstr "Strojno dekodiranje"

#: src/qml/Settings/PlaybackSettings.qml:149
msgctxt "@info:tooltip hardware decoding setting"
msgid ""
"Specify the hardware video decoding API that should be used if possible. "
"Whether hardware decoding is actually done depends on the video codec. If "
"hardware decoding is not possible, mpv will fall back on software decoding."
"<br><br><ul><li><strong>auto</strong> tries to automatically enable hardware "
"decoding using the first available method.</li><li><strong>auto-safe</"
"strong> similar to auto, but allows only whitelisted methods that are "
"considered “safe”.</li><li><strong>vaapi</strong> works with Intel and AMD "
"GPUs only. It also requires the opengl EGL backend.</li><li><strong>nvdec</"
"strong> the newest, and recommended method to do hardware decoding on Nvidia "
"GPUs.</li><li><strong>cuda</strong> an older implementation of hardware "
"decoding on Nvidia GPUs.</li><li><strong>videotoolbox</strong></"
"li><li><strong>d3d11va</strong></li></ul><br><br>You can read more about "
"hardware decoding here: <a href='https://mpv.io/manual/stable/#options-"
"hwdec'>https://mpv.io/manual/stable/#options-hwdec</a><br><br>You can set "
"another hardware decoder by creating a startup custom command <strong>set "
"hwdec <i>decoder_name</i></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Določi strojni API za dekodiranje videoposnetkov, ki ga je treba uporabiti, "
"če je mogoče. Ali je strojno dekodiranje dejansko izvedeno, je odvisno od "
"video kodeka. Če strojno dekodiranje ni mogoče, bo mpv uporabil programsko "
"dekodiranje.<br><br><ul><li><strong>auto</strong> poskuša samodejno "
"omogočiti strojno dekodiranje s prvo razpoložljivo metodo.</li "
"><li><strong>auto-safe</strong> podobno kot samodejno, vendar dovoljuje samo "
"metode s seznama dovoljenih, ki veljajo za \"varne\".</li><li><strong>vaapi</"
"strong> deluje z Intelom in samo grafični procesorji AMD. Zahteva tudi "
"zaledje opengl EGL.</li><li><strong>nvdec</strong> najnovejša in priporočena "
"metoda za dekodiranje strojne opreme na grafičnih procesorjih Nvidia.</"
"li><li><strong>cuda</ strong> starejša izvedba dekodiranja strojne opreme na "
"grafičnih procesorjih Nvidia.</li><li><strong>videotoolbox</strong></"
"li><li><strong>d3d11va</strong></li></ul> <br><br>Več o dekodiranju strojne "
"opreme lahko preberete tukaj: <a href='https://mpv.io/manual/stable/#options-"
"hwdec'>https://mpv.io/manual/stable/#options-hwdec</a><br><br>Drug "
"dekodirnik strojne opreme lahko nastavite tako, da ustvarite zagonski ukaz "
"po meri <strong>set hwdec <i>decoder_name</i></strong>."

