#: src/qml/Settings/VideoSettings.qml:163
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Specify the filename template used to save screenshots. The template "
"specifies the filename without file extension, and can contain format "
"specifiers, which will be substituted when taking a screenshot. By default, "
"the template is “%F-%n”. <br>The template can start with a relative or "
"absolute path, in order to specify a directory location where screenshots "
"should be saved.<br>If the final screenshot filename points to an already "
"existing file, the file will not be overwritten. The screenshot will either "
"not be saved, or if the template contains %n, saved using different, newly "
"generated filename.<br>For full info checkout <a href='https://mpv.io/manual/"
"stable/#options-screenshot-template'>https://mpv.io/manual/stable/#options-"
"screenshot-template</a><br><br><strong>Allowed format specifiers:</"
"strong><br><ul><li><strong>%[#][0X]n</strong> A sequence number, padded with "
"zeros to length X.<br><li><strong>%f</strong> Filename of the currently "
"played video.<br><li><strong>%F</strong> Same as %f, but without the file "
"extension.<br><li><strong>%x</strong> Directory path of the currently played "
"video. If the video is not on the filesystem (http:// urls), this expands to "
"an empty string.<br><li><strong>%X{fallback}</strong> Same as %x, but if the "
"video file is not on the filesystem, return the fallback string inside the "
"{…}.<br><li><strong>%p</strong> Current playback time. The result is a "
"string of the form “HH:MM:SS”.<br><li><strong>%P</strong> Similar to %p, but "
"extended with the playback time in milliseconds “HH:MM:SS.mmm”."
"<br><li><strong>%wX</strong> Specify the current playback time using the "
"format string X.<br>Valid format specifiers:<br><ul><li><strong>%wH</strong> "
"hour (padded with 0 to two digits)</li><li><strong>%wh</strong> hour (not "
"padded)</li><li><strong>%wM</strong> minutes (00–59)</li><li><strong>%wm</"
"strong> total minutes (includes hours, unlike %wM)</li><li><strong>%wS</"
"strong> seconds (00–59)</li><li><strong>%ws</strong> total seconds (includes "
"hours and minutes)</li><li><strong>%wf</strong> like %ws, but as float</"
"li><li><strong>%wT</strong> milliseconds (000–999)</li><li><strong>%%</"
"strong> Replaced with the % character itself.</li></ul><br>"
msgstr ""
"Določi predlogo imena datoteke, ki se uporablja za shranjevanje posnetkov "
"zaslona. Predloga podaja ime datoteke brez datotečne pripone in lahko "
"vsebuje določilnike formata, ki bodo zamenjani pri posnetku zaslona. "
"Privzeto je predloga \"%F-%n\". <br>Predloga se lahko začne z relativno ali "
"absolutno potjo, da določi lokacijo imenika, kamor naj se shranijo posnetki "
"zaslona.<br>Če končno ime datoteke posnetka zaslona kaže na že obstoječo "
"datoteko, datoteka ne bo prepisana. Posnetek zaslona ne bo shranjen ali če "
"predloga vsebuje %n, shranjen z drugim, na novo ustvarjenim imenom datoteke."
"<br>Za vse informacije preverite <a href='https://mpv.io/manual/stable/"
"#options -screenshot-template'>https://mpv.io/manual/stable/#options-"
"screenshot-template</a><br><br><strong>Dovoljeni določilniki oblike:</"
"strong><br><ul ><li><strong>%[#][0X]n</strong> Zaporedna številka, obložena "
"z ničlami ​​do dolžine X.<br><li><strong>%f</strong> Ime datoteke, ki se "
"trenutno predvaja video.<br><li><strong>%F</strong> Enako kot %f, vendar "
"brez datotečne pripone.<br><li><strong>%x</strong> Pot imenika trenutno "
"predvajanega videoposnetka . Če videoposnetka ni v datotečnem sistemu "
"(http:// urls), se to razširi v prazen niz.<br><li><strong>%X{fallback}</"
"strong> Enako kot %x, vendar če video datoteke ni v datotečnem sistemu, vrne "
"nadomestni niz znotraj {…}.<br><li><strong>%p</strong> Trenutni čas "
"predvajanja. Rezultat je niz v obliki \"HH:MM:SS\".<br><li><strong>%P</"
"strong> Podobno %p, vendar razširjeno s časom predvajanja v milisekundah "
"\"HH:MM:SS.mmm\".<br><li><strong>%wX</strong> Določi trenutni čas "
"predvajanja z nizom oblike X.<br>Veljavni določilnik oblike:"
"<br><ul><li><strong>% wH</strong> ura (dopolnjeno z 0 do dvema števkama)</"
"li><li><strong>%wh</strong> ura (ni dopolnjeno)</li><li><strong>%wM</strong "
"> minut (00-59)</li><li><strong>%wm</strong> skupno minut (vključuje ure, za "
"razliko od %wM)</li><li><strong>%wS</strong> sekund (00-59)</li><li><strong>"
"%ws</strong> skupno število sekund (vključno z urami in minutami)</"
"li><li><strong>%wf</strong> kot %ws, vendar kot float</li><li><strong>%wT</"
"strong> milisekunde (000-999)</li><li><strong>%%</strong> Zamenjano s samim "
"znakom %.</li ></ul><br>"

